{{> layout/header}}

<style>
    .role-section { padding: 72px 28px 80px; }
    .role-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .role-title { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 900; color: #1c1e26; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .role-desc { font-size: 14px; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .role-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; }
    .role-card { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #eaecf4; border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 24px; cursor: pointer; transition: all .15s; }
    .role-card:hover { border-color: #2563eb; transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37,99,235,.1); }
    .role-icon { font-size: 44px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .role-name { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; color: #1c1e26; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .role-sub { font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.6; }
    .role-card button { display:none; }
    .role-hint { margin-top: 28px; font-size: 13px; color: #c4c9d9; }
</style>

<section class="role-section">
    <div class="role-inner">
        <h1 class="role-title">SevMerge를 어떻게 이용하시겠어요?</h1>
        <p class="role-desc">가입 이후에도 마이페이지에서 전문가 신청을 할 수 있어요.</p>

        <div class="role-cards">
            <form action="/kakao-join" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="role" value="CLIENT" />
                <div class="role-card" onclick="this.closest('form').submit()">
                    <div class="role-icon">💼</div>
                    <div class="role-name">의뢰인으로 이용</div>
                    <div class="role-sub">프로젝트를 등록하고<br>전문가를 찾고 싶어요</div>
                </div>
            </form>

            <form action="/kakao-join" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="role" value="EXPERT" />
                <div class="role-card" onclick="this.closest('form').submit()">
                    <div class="role-icon">👨‍💻</div>
                    <div class="role-name">전문가로 활동</div>
                    <div class="role-sub">프로젝트에 제안서를 보내고<br>수익을 창출하고 싶어요</div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <p class="role-hint">카드를 클릭하면 선택한 유형으로 가입돼요.</p>
    </div>
</section>

{{> layout/footer}}